            <div class="breakout">
              <p>MyService uses a document uploads pattern for forms </p>
              <h2>Rules:</h2>
              <ul>
                <li>
                  When a document is successfully uploaded, the categories status turns to success
                </li>
                <li>When a document category has a success status, its default accordion position is always closed when viewed
                  on subsequent pages</li>
                <li>When a document category is in a required state, its default position is always open</li>
              </ul>
